Daily Devotional Songs:

* Vishnu Tamil Devotional Songs: Immerse in the blessings of Lord Vishnu.
* Muruga Tamil Devotional Songs: Invoke the valor and blessings of Lord Muruga.
* Hanuman Tamil Devotional Songs: Feel the strength and devotion of Lord Hanuman.
* Amman Tamil Devotional Songs: Honor the divine mother in her various forms.
* Saibaba Tamil Devotional Songs: Seek the blessings of Shirdi Sai Baba.

* Lakshmi Tamil Devotional Songs: Attract prosperity with hymns for Goddess Lakshmi.
* Devi Tamil Devotional Songs: Praise the supreme goddess Devi in her many avatars.
* Ganesh Tamil Devotional Songs: Start your day with prayers to Lord Ganesha.

Special Occasions and Deities:
* Amavasai Tamil Devotional Songs: Songs for the new moon day rituals.
* Pradosham Tamil Devotional Songs: Hymns for the auspicious Pradosham period.
* Ashta Lakshmi Tamil Devotional Songs: Songs dedicated to the eight forms of Goddess Lakshmi.
* Vinayagar Tamil Devotional Songs: Devotions for the remover of obstacles, Lord Vinayagar.
* Ganapathi Tamil Devotional Songs: Invoke blessings from Lord Ganapathi.
* Surya Tamil Devotional Songs: Worship the Sun God, Surya, with these melodies.
* Sani Tamil Devotional Songs: Appease Lord Sani with these devotional tracks.
* Guru Tamil Devotional Songs: Songs to honor Guru and seek his wisdom.
* Perumal Tamil Devotional Songs: Devote to Lord Perumal with these spiritual songs.
* Navagraha Tamil Devotional Songs: Balance your energies with songs for the nine planets.

Subscribe now and join our spiritual journey. Like, share, and hit the bell icon to stay updated with our latest devotional uploads. May these divine songs bring peace, prosperity, and positivity to your life.

snippet.title: Mowgli Trailer | Roshan Kanakala | Bandi Saroj Kumar | Sandeep Raj | Sakkshi | TG Vishwa Prasad
snippet.description:
Mowgli 2025 will arrive in cinemas on December 12th, 2025.

Mowgli is an upcoming 2025 unique romantic action drama set deep within a forest backdrop. Directed by National Award-winning filmmaker Sandeep Raj (Colour Photo), Produced by TG Vishwa Prasad and Krithi Prasad under People Media Factory Banner.The film has cinematography by Rama Maruthi M, while Kaala Bhairava scores the music. The work is co-written by Rama Maruthi M and Radhakrishna Reddy The technical team also includes Peekay as editor, Kiran Mamidi as art director, and Natraj Madigonda choreographing the action sequences.

Topics to be covered in the live stream üëáüèªüëáüèªüëáüèª

India vs South Africa Live Match Today
india vs South Africa Live
India vs South Africa 2nd ODI Live Cricket Score 
IND vs SA Live Match Today
IND vs SA Cricket Live Match Today 
Live Cricket Match Today 
Cricket Live


When: Wednesday, December 3, 2025 at 1:30 PM IST

Where: Shaheed Veer Narayan Singh International Stadium, Raipur

What to expect: Clear skies are expected for the game. The only ODI that was played here saw India's pacers skittle New Zealand out for just 118.

Rohit hit a majestic ton to close out the Australia series in fantastic fashion and Kohli hit a fifty in the same game after registering two ducks before that. On Sunday, the two players stood tall once again and this time it was Kohli's turn to go past three figures. Undoubtedly, the capacity crowd would want this streak to continue, especially if they take into account the fact that they might not see these two play live in front of them again. This venue has hosted only two international matches so far and there are no guarantees the star duo would still be active by the time Raipur hosts another international fixture.

The team management would also want runs from the likes of Yashasvi Jaiswal and Ruturaj Gaikwad after the duo had middling outings on their return to ODI cricket. While there could be concerns around their inability to close out the game comfortably after having South Africa 5 down very early in a tall run chase, the visitors definitely deserve credit for their fightback.

Matthew Breetzke, Marco Jansen and later Colin Bosch showcased that it's never over until it's over in this day and age especially in a format where there's always plenty of time to claw back. If they had held their nerves in the final 10 overs, South Africa could have easily chased down 350 to send a statement. But now that's behind them, the immediate focus will be on stopping the Ro-Ko juggernaut to give themselves the best chance of levelling the series.

Team News

India: The hosts will likely stick to the same combination and that means another opportunity for Yashasvi Jaiswal and Ruturaj Gaikwad. It will be interesting to see if they stick to using Washington Sundar at 5 or swap slots with Ravindra Jadeja.

Probable XI: Yashavi Jaiswal, Rohit Sharma, Virat Kohli, Ruturaj Gaikwad, Washington Sundar, KL Rahul (C & WK), Ravindra Jadeja, Harshit Rana, Kuldeep Yadav, Arshdeep Singh, Prasidh Krishna

South Africa: For the visitors, Temba Bavuma should be back after being rested for the first game. Ryan Rickelton will be expected to make way with Quinton de Kock returning to the top of the order. Keshav Maharaj could come in for Prenelan Subrayen.

Probable XI: Quinton de Kock (WK), Aiden Markram, Temba Bavuma (C), Matthew Breetzke, Tony de Zorzi, Dewald Brevis, Marco Jansen, Corbin Bosch, Keshav Maharaj, Nandre Burger, Ottneil Baartman.

India vs South Africa Highlights Today
India have to play almost 10 T20i Matches before the ICC Men's T20 Cricket World Cup 2026. This is an opportunity to maintain momentum & chose the best 11 players for upcoming event. After the 3 match ODI Series, India will play 5 T20 Match Matches against South Africa at home. Afterwards, New Zealand cricket team will visit India.

Here is the teams list that will participate in the next T20 World Cup 2026.

T20 World Cup 2026 teams and groups
Group A: India, Pakistan, Netherlands, Namibia, USA.
Group B: Sri Lanka, Australia, Zimbabwe, Ireland, Oman.
Group C: England, West Indies, Bangladesh, Nepal. Italy.
Group D: South Africa, New Zealand, Afghanistan, UAE, Canada. India vs Pakistan T20 Cricket World Cup Match Will be played on February 15 2026.

snippet.title: Jaliba Mo Jui || Prem Darshan || Pushpa || Humane Sagar || Odia Music Video || Enewsodia
snippet.description:
üíî ‚ÄúAji Rati Gale Pahi Jaliba Mo Jui‚Äù is a heart-touching Odia sad song that reflects the pain of separation, unspoken feelings, and emotional heartbreak sang by Humane Sagar. The soulful voice and emotional lyrics beautifully bring out the depth of love that has been lost, making this track relatable for anyone who has experienced sadness in love.The song captures the journey of someone who still cherishes their beloved (Jui ‚Äì meaning the light of life) even after distance and destiny have created a painful gap. Its melody, music arrangement, and emotional expression make it a powerful sad song that stays with listeners long after it ends.

snippet.title: RISING CHAMPIONSHIP SEASON 1 - PRE QUARTERS G4  @JONATHANGAMINGYT @S8ULGG @OMEGAAAA @SaumRaj
snippet.description:
RISING CHAMPIONSHIP SEASON 1 - PRE QUARTER FINAL G4

SIXTEEN TEAMS.
SIX MAP.

snippet.title: Seet Lehar - Filmy (Official Music Video) Ft. Tanu Rawat | New Haryanvi Song 2025 | Real Music
snippet.description:
Presenting the new Haryanvi song 2025 ‚Äì Seet Lehar (Dekh Le) by Filmy Ft. Tanu Rawat | Real Music 
Seet Lehar Filmy | Dekh Le Filmy

Feel the winter breeze of love with ‚ÄúSeet Lehar‚Äù, a refreshing Haryanvi romantic-pop track by Filmy, featuring Tanu Rawat.
With soothing vocals, nostalgic melodies, and cinematic visuals, this song captures the essence of cold-season romance ‚Äî cozy moments, heartfelt emotions, and timeless chemistry.

‚ÄúSeet Lehar‚Äù brings together modern Haryanvi music and retro charm, blending soft synths, catchy rhythms, and pure lyrical warmth. Whether it‚Äôs a foggy morning or a starry winter night, this song will melt your heart every time.

Cold wind. Warm hearts. Pure Haryanvi vibe.
Experience the magic of love, nostalgia, and melody ‚Äî only on Real Music.

Song Lyrics:
Dekhle Han  Challa Seet Lehar Tere Sehahar 
Dehle Ra Mausam Ya Horyaa Kati Jehar Dekh Le 
Dekhle Tu Kaadh Ka Rajai Mein Ta Pair Dekh Le 
Dekhle Koi Bhana Laaka Aa Saka Ja Bher 

Chord Cupa Na Piladu Tana Khullad Ki Chaa 
Girya Taapman Teri Jad Jhuki Thi Nigaa 
Bhare Khore Mein Dikhe Tere Ghar Aali Raah 
Koi Mere Jaise Aashiq Tu Dhund Ka Dikha 

Aaka Jaa Liye December Ye Phla Bhi Bade 
Tere Rup Na Kare Ye Mere Rongte Khade 
Aaj Ta Phla Ye Nain Kitte Ni Lade 
Lade Tere Ta To Raha Ge Yaar Pade Ke Pade 

Dekhle  Ya Moka Baar Baar Ni Milega 
Dekhle Han Mere Jaise Yaar Ni Milega 
Dekhle Han Milya Bhi To Pyaar Ni Milega 
Dekhle Koi Aisa Dildaar Ni Milega 

Dekhle Han  Challa Seet Lehar Tere Sehahar 
Dehle Ra Mausam Ya Horyaa Kati Jehar Dekh Le 
Dekhle Tu Kaadh Ka Rajai Mein Ta Pair Dekh Le 
Dekhle Koi Bhana Laaka Aa Saka Ja Bher 

Kade Dekhiye Jaade Mein Mahre Gaam Ka Nazara 
Jama Senery Sa Lagga Dikha Dur Ta Hi Pyara 
Bund Oos Ki Kehta Pa Kara Motia Na Fail 
Aaake Bethiye Sarhane Jama Tata Padya Hara 

Tu Baat Thodi Kara Tu Chakti Chala 
Tu Fulla Ki Trah Han Mehkti Chala 
Haye Sachi Sachi Bata Seekhya Kada Ta Ye Jadu 
Tu Bhakaaye Java Budhi Meri Bhakti Chala 

Dekhle Hai Teri Ichha Jorr Koni Koye 
Dekhle Mera Bhi Adda Aur Koni Koye 
Dekhle Tu Kalje Mein Chor Koni Koye 
Dekhle Chalange Jit Shorr Koni Koye 

Dekhle Han  Challa Seet Lehar Tere Sehahar 
Dehle Ra Mausam Ya Horyaa Kati Jehar Dekh Le 
Dekhle Tu Kaadh Ka Rajai Mein Ta Pair Dekh Le 
Dekhle Koi Bhana Laaka Aa Saka Ja Bher

snippet.description:
üåü Celebrating the 86th Birth Anniversary of the Legendary R.D. Burman üåü

On the iconic occasion of R.D. Burman‚Äôs 86th birth anniversary, we present one of his most timeless and melodious creations ‚Äî "Chura Liya Hai Tumne Jo Dil Ko" from the film Yaadon Ki Baaraat (1973). A musical gem that has captivated generations with its dreamy tune and soulful voices of Asha Bhosle and Mohammed Rafi.

Featuring the ever-charming Zeenat Aman, this evergreen romantic number showcases Pancham Da‚Äôs genius in blending western instrumentation with Indian melody. Let‚Äôs relive this golden classic and pay tribute to the master of melodies ‚Äî Rahul Dev Burman.

Franklin goes back to the Leaf Village and informs Hashirama, Kakashi and Shinchan. All of them open a portal to the Brainrots base where the Brainrot secret map is kept. With ninja powers shared by Naruto, Franklin enters full ninja mode and defeats the Brainrots to save everyone.

snippet.title: NZ vs WI | 1st Test Day 2 | Highlights | West Indies Tour Of New Zealand 2025
snippet.description:
New Zealand's bowlers, notably Jacob Duffy who took a five-wicket haul, rattled the West Indies middle and lower order, dismissing them for 167 after the West Indies had resumed at 157/6 after a rain delay.
